    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Compute the NAV for an account.\\n\\nLoops all registered positions, calls each adapter's\\n`get_all_position_values(account, oracle_registry)`, and sums up\\nasset vs debt values in USDC (6 decimals, scale = 1_000_000).",
